Deutsche Post to Use Electric Cars for Mail Delivery, FAZ Says

-- B y   A n d r e a s   C r e m e r
-- 
2011-09-11T17:39:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-11/deutsche-post-to-use-electric-cars-for-mail-delivery-faz-says.html
Deutsche Post AG will switch to
using electric transportation for mail delivery and has mandated
Streetscooter GmbH, a German carmaker, to develop a battery-
powered vehicle by the fall of 2012,  Frankfurter Allgemeine
Zeitung  reported, without citing a source for the information.  Bonn, Germany-based Deutsche Post could order as many as
20,000 units of the vehicle, the newspaper said  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andreas Cremer in Berlin at 
 acremer@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas at 
 cthomas16@bloomberg.net  